name: **Leaghillaun**
description: Leaghillaun V584-586 Sheet 83 / Sheet 84 Lovely but ungrazed and overgrown islet just off a beautiful strand in W Castle Cove. The channel on the W side is deep at all stages of the tide. Rabbits. Land at the beach on the NW side, directly off the beach. Launch from the beach in front of the Derrynane Rowing Club.
